# Git workflow (agents)

- Do not create a new Git branch unless the user explicitly requests it (for example by naming the branch or clearly instructing you to create a branch for the work).
- Default to working on the current branch unless the user specifies a different branch or workflow.
- Do not initiate feature-branch or multi-branch workflows on your own; follow explicit Git instructions only.
